	4. Install xorg environment

	$ pacman -S xorg-server xorg-server-utils xorg-xinit
	$ pacman -S xorg-twm xorg-xclock xterm
	$ startx  ------->test its working
	to close xorg type exit in any of the open windows

5. Install DE(desktop environment)

	$ pacman -S xfce4 xfce4-goodies

	6. install openbox

	$ sudo pacman -S openbox tint2 nitrogen oblogout
	$ sudo pacman -S lxappearance

